name: Rhino-Lip: GoPro: Go TOUGH!....or just go home.
description:
ATTENTION

PLEASE READ BEFORE PLACING ORDER

Fitting kit included

The hardware kit is recommended but it is ultimately the decision of the buyer on how to fit Rhino Lip to the vehicle.

**Message us On Whether You need more than the standard 8' ft  (2.43m's) Measure of Product that comes per Order, 
.....we'll get it taken care of for you: No Hassles!

Since '07 Rhino-Lip, Dura-Flex Bumper-Guard Lip has been focused with the goal of providing protection & improved stance on YOUR vehicle for a reasonable price.

The Rhino Lip is a USA Manufactured TOUGH, Resilient, Durable Long-Lasting Auto-Accessory.

It is NOT made like the QWiK Cheap & E-Z Squishy Chinese Manufactured E-Z QWiK Lip (Which we can provide samples of to compare to the Rhino-Lip).

No QWiK & E-Z 10 Minute 3 Step "Tape" Install here with our product either.

"Tape" doesn't last nor hold up.

If it did? OEM Manufacturers would install Bumper Covers & all sorts of Auto-Accessories with "Tape": But they DON'T.

We think those well educated Engineers Know some things.

MORE THAN ENOUGH INFO IN OUR BIG CARTEL INFO PAGES!!.

Free Sample-Packs Available: Compare Quality BEFORE you Buy!
